               <msContents>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; names of the donor and his family members; groups of
                        lines on the incipit page, incipits of all sections and subsections;
                        elements of the punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic numerals.</rubric>
                     <incipit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="coloph1">
                     <colophon>
                        <locus target="47rb"/>Fol. 47rb l.6: ዝንቱ፡ ድርሳን፡
                        ፲ወ፪፡ አውረኅ፡ ፲ወ፪፡ ተአምር፡ ለሊቀ፡ መላእክት፡ ተጽሕፈ፡ በዘመኑ፡ ለወንጌላዊ፡ ሉቃስ። ወበመንግሥቱ፡ ለንጉሥነ፡
                        ዮሐንስ፡ ወጳጳስነ፡ አባ፡ ጴጥሮስ፡ ከመ፡ ይኩነኒ፡ ...<foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                        <note>The colophon states that the Ms. was written during the reign of King
                           Yoḥannǝs IV (r. 1872-89) and during the tenure of Metropolitan Ṗeṭros IV
                           (1881-1917).</note>
                     </colophon>
                  </msItem>
